      </div>
      <div class="group studies">
        <h2 class="section-title">Studies</h2>
        <div class="items">
          <div class="study">
            <h3>
              Technical Degree in Programming <span>06/2024 - Present</span>
            </h3>
            <p>
              I am beginning a Technical Degree in Programming at UTN. My
              studies focus on developing skills to analyze and solve software
